    "description": "▼始皇帝や白起など春秋戦国時代の有名人を井上和彦さん、小清水亜美さん、森田成一さん、杉山紀彰さん一流声優が熱演!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/64838c56418eccff7acd9c935490b816.avif?t=1676260778\" width=618 height=588 /></span><br><br>▼ 三国志より500年以前の壮大な時代が舞台、斬新な歴史テーマが戦国の七雄をリアルに再現します<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/cd9dd38940a0dc6f872d8f91866ff510.avif?t=1676260778\" width=618 height=588 /></span><br><br>▼春秋戦国時代の有名人物を育成し、自分だけ武将編成を作り、天下統一を目指そう!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/0f0191c0fac8b9a7661fa8139d38432f.avif?t=1676260778\" width=618 height=588 /></span><br><br>▼サクサク爽快なリアルタイムバトル<br>- ターン制ではありません、瞬時の作戦操作で勝利を手にできます<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/e15626180bef78c00489e180b1a8e4db.poster.avif?t=1676260778\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/e15626180bef78c00489e180b1a8e4db.webm?t=1676260778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/e15626180bef78c00489e180b1a8e4db.mp4?t=1676260778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>▼多兵種·多武器、組み合わせ自由度MAX！策略を使って、無限の戦闘可能性を追求しよう！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/9a5c27e59c18c92dc07cd691097131df.poster.avif?t=1676260778\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154840/extras/9a5c27e59c18c92dc07cd691097131df.webm?t=1676260778\" type=\"